      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade vehicle of unparalleled caliber. This specimen has been preserved in showroom-original state, exhibiting flawless paintwork and an interior that remains entirely indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and subjected to an exhaustive mechanical certification, this automobile represents the pinnacle of its class. We invite the most exacting collectors to experience a vehicle that defines automotive excellence.",
