    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it strictly in the garage, and never missed a service. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
