      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve pampered it since day one, always kept it garaged, and there\u2019s not a single blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you want a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
