      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically flawless example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a perfectly calibrated VANOS system and crisp individual throttle bodies, delivering peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been meticulously maintained with reinforced subframe mounts and refreshed bushings, preserving its original torsional rigidity. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero fluid leaks, impeccable compression, and a pristine undercarriage, representing the absolute apex of the analog driving experience.",
